				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544">
					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Fresh mussels can be used instead of dried mussels. Or parseley can be used instead of garlic and /or ginger, and butter instead of sesame oil.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Some components of garlic, particularly alliin, scorsine, and allicin, have medicinal effects. Allicin is an odorous compound with antibiotic effect and is produced when minced.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
